<%- include("../partials/header"); -%>

<section>

  <!-- Cover image -->
  <div>
    <img src="/images/course-cover/course-cover-flotilla-skipper-training.jpg" width="100%" class="top-image" alt="course-cover-flotilla-skipper-training">
  </div>

  <div class="container-fluid course-background">
    <div class="course-sheet">

      <!-- Course title -->
      <div class="course-title">
        <h1><b>Flotilla Skipper Training</b></h1>
        <p class="lead course-subtitle"><em>Join us for flotilla sailing, either sailing / motoring in your own or one of our charter boats around the Maltese islands, or even longer trips to Sicily, Lampedusa, Pantelleria, Tunisia or even Croatia. Bring the family and friends, and have the comfort factor of a fully qualified and experienced instructor nearby.</em></p>
        <br><br>
      </div>

      <!-- Course calendar section: dont change below -->
      <div class="course-calendar">
        <h3><b>Upcoming Course Dates</b></h3>
        <div class="row">

          <!-- months tabs -->
          <div class="col-xl-3 col-lg-3 calendar-month">
            <div class="list-group" id="list-tab" role="tablist">
              <%  uniqueMonthsYears.forEach(function(uniqueMonthYear,index) {%>
              <a class="list-group-item list-group-item-action <% if(index===0) {%> <%="active"%> <%}%>" id="list-<%=uniqueMonthYear%>-list" data-toggle="list" href="#list-<%=uniqueMonthYear%>" role="tab"><%=uniqueMonthYear%></a>
              <%})%>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="col-xl-6 col-lg-9">
            <div class="tab-content" id="nav-tabContent">
              <%- include("../partials/calendar-pop-up"); -%>

              <div class="calendar-buttons">
                <p><b>This course is organized on request. Please contact us or send us an enquiry if you're interested. üòâ‚Äç</b></p>
                <a class="btn btn-primary course-four-bottom" href="/contact#enquiry-form" role="button">Send us an enquiry &raquo;</a>
                <a class="btn btn-warning  course-four-bottom" href="/booking/courses/<%=courseName%>" role="button">Book now &raquo;</a>
                <% if(courseProfileFound.onlineLink != "") {%>
                <a href="<%=courseProfileFound.onlineLink%>" class="btn btn-info course-four-bottom" role="button">Online course &raquo;</a>
                <%}%>
                <% if(courseProfileFound.ryaLink != "") {%>
                <a href="<%=courseProfileFound.ryaLink%>" class="btn btn-light course-four-bottom" role="button"><img src="/images/RYA_logo.png" width="50"></a>
                <%}%>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- the map -->
          <%- include("../partials/maps/manoel"); -%>

              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Course detail accordion -->
            <div class="accordion" id="accordionExample">

              <div class="card">
                <div class="card-header" id="headingOne">
                  <h2 class="mb-0">
                    <button class="btn btn-link" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseOne" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseOne">
                      Course Description
                    </button>
                  </h2>
                </div>

                <div id="collapseOne" class="collapse show" aria-labelledby="headingOne" data-parent="#accordionExample">
                  <div class="card-body">
                    <p> Joining a ‚Äúflotilla‚Äù is a fun and exciting way to learn how to confidently skipper a charter yacht for the very first time. A group of boats sail together (flotilla) along a set route, with a ‚Äúlead boat‚Äù in charge, overseeing the safety of all the boats where all the boats are within range of a VHF radio call if required. Before departing in the morning, a route is planned for the day with a set destination for the evenings so that all the boats can anchor or tie up to a mooring buoy (before dark) for the night. Generally speaking, flotillas are restricted to passages close to shore, in fair weather and in good visibility. They are usually followed in the evenings by a beach bar-b-que or dinner together in a social atmosphere where students can swap stories and learn from each other. It is a great way to make new friends and build your confidence, while still enjoying the freedom of being in command of your own vessel with your family and friends.
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="card">
                <div class="card-header" id="headingTwo">
                  <h2 class="mb-0">
                    <button class="btn btn-link collapsed" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseTwo" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseTwo">
                      Course Requirements
                    </button>
                  </h2>
                </div>
                <div id="collapseTwo" class="collapse show" aria-labelledby="headingTwo" data-parent="#accordionExample">
                  <div class="card-body">
                    <p> The recommended entry level requirement for the Flotilla Skipper course are the RYA Day Skipper and the RYA Marine Radio VHF. The candidate should be 16 years of age or over.
                    </p>

                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

            </div>

            <%- include("../partials/reviews"); -%>
            <!-- Bottom buttons -->
            <div class="course-bottom-buttons">
              <a class="btn btn-primary course-four-bottom" href="/contact#enquiry-form" role="button">Send us an enquiry &raquo;</a>
              <a class="btn btn-warning course-four-bottom" href="/booking/courses/<%=courseName%>" role="button">Book now &raquo;</a>
              <% if(courseProfileFound.onlineLink != "") {%>
              <a href="<%=courseProfileFound.onlineLink%>" class="btn btn-info course-four-bottom" role="button">Online course &raquo;</a>
              <%}%>
        <% if(courseProfileFound.ryaLink != "") {%>
              <a href="<%=courseProfileFound.ryaLink%>" class="btn btn-light course-four-bottom" role="button"><img src="/images/RYA_logo.png" width="50"></a>
              <%}%>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>

</section>

<%- include("../partials/footer"); -%>